- [License](#license)

## Features

- User Authentication
  - Secure login and registration
  - JWT-based authentication
- User Profiles
  - Manage user and business profiles
- Business Management
  - Create and manage business listings
  - Showcase products and services
- Search Functionality
  - Search for businesses, products, and services
- Responsive Design
  - Mobile-first design approach
- State Management
  - Using Redux for global state management
- Cloud Integration
  - Azure cloud services integration

## Tech Stack

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Mongoose
- JWT for authentication
- bcrypt for password hashing

### Frontend
- React.js
- Redux
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js and npm
- MongoDB
- Git

### Installation

Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Kitsao16/business-platform.git
cd business-platform

